Detailed Description

cvmx_tra::_read_dat

TRA_READ_DAT = Trace Buffer Read Data

Description:

Notes: This CSR is a memory of 1024 entries. When the trace was enabled, the read pointer was set to entry 0 by hardware. Each read to this address increments the read pointer.
